<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think that is there for reference. It can be interesting to have a look at the original Buddhist texts, but they are obviously much harder to penetr<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think that is there for reference. It can be interesting to have a look at the original Buddhist texts, but they are obviously much harder to penetrate, being written in an ancient language a long time ago. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
